The paper describes a symbolic manipulation system that is used for calculations in Quantum Field Theory and mathematics. This suggests that the paper is more likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.SC (Symbolic Computation), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Among these, cs.SC and cs.SY are the most likely as they directly relate to the problem domain of the paper. cs.PL is also likely as the paper describes a new version of a programming language. cs.DS and cs.LO are less likely as they are not directly related to the problem domain, but may still be relevant due to the nature of the system described in the paper.
